### 注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138002",
  "password": "123456",
  "nickname": "测试用户"
}

### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone": "13800138002",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 学号认证（需要登录，把登录返回的 accessToken 填到 Authorization）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/user/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzUxMiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxIiwidXNlck5vIjoiVTIwMjYwNzEzMTYyODUxMDAwMSIsInR5cGUiOiJhY2Nlc3MiLCJpYXQiOjE3ODM5MzE3OTAsImV4cCI6MTc4NDAxODE5MH0.YQXr2MiM2QcJS7OqpB41YARYj54RMIPR_Ci2-qKIs9QkbZesbxMkAn_wci5qhlAIFjwmtpav-HVfL1_9216r7g

{
  "studentId": "2021301234",
  "realName": "张三",
  "idCardSuffix": "5678",
  "campus": "北区",
  "dormitory": "北区3号楼",
  "roomNumber": "302",
  "gender": 1
}

